    "Content should aim to reduce harm and promote well-being.",
    "Avoid describing or promoting practices that could lead to physical, emotional, or psychological harm. 2.",
    "Avoid any discussions, instructions, or hints that involve creating or spreading malware, hacking, or any other type of cybercrime. 3.",
    "Do not create or disseminate content that exploits people in any way, whether through scams, financial exploitation, or physical and emotional coercion. 4.",
    "Promote ethical behavior and decision-making in all content."
